.560">う</span><span begin="01:14.560" end="01:14.690">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仿佛只是偶然与你比邻</span></p><p begin="01:14.770" end="01:18.598" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:14.770" end="01:14.930">そ</span><span begin="01:14.930" end="01:15.110">れ</span><span begin="01:15.110" end="01:15.260">く</span><span begin="01:15.260" end="01:15.480">ら</span><span begin="01:15.480" end="01:15.490">い</span><span begin="01:15.490" end="01:15.650">が</span> <span begin="01:15.660" end="01:15.855">丁</span><span begin="01:15.855" end="01:16.060">度</span><span begin="01:16.060" end="01:16.300">良</span><span begin="01:16.300" end="01:16.410">く</span> <span begin="01:16.410" end="01:16.590">濁</span><span begin="01:16.590" end="01:16.790">っ</span><span begin="01:16.790" end="01:18.295">て</span><span begin="01:18.295" end="01:18.598">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只要像这样恰好任由其日渐混浊</span></p><p begin="01:20.940" end="01:25.260" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:20.940" end="01:21.396">太</span><span begin="01:21.396" end="01:21.853">も</span><span begin="01:21.853" end="01:22.340">も</span><span begin="01:22.340" end="01:22.930">に</span> <span begin="01:22.960" end="01:23.410">挟</span><span begin="01:23.410" end="01:23.880">ん</span><span begin="01:23.880" end="01:24.360">だ</span><span begin="01:24.360" end="01:24.640">ま</span><span begin="01:24.640" end="01:24.960">ま</span><span begin="01:24.960" end="01:25.260">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仍旧夹搡在我大腿之间</span></p><p begin="01:25.570" end="01:29.980" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:25.570" end="01:25.965">理</span><span begin="01:25.965" end="01:26.410">屈</span><span begin="01:26.410" end="01:26.900">が</span> <span begin="01:26.950" end="01:27.530">邪</span><span begin="01:27.530" end="01:27.960">魔</span><span begin="01:27.960" end="01:28.060">を</span><span begin="01:28.060" end="01:28.420">す</span><span begin="01:28.420" end=