" end="01:42.090">て</span><span begin="01:42.090" end="01:42.220">に</span><span begin="01:42.220" end="01:42.350">な</span><span begin="01:42.350" end="01:42.690">ら</span><span begin="01:42.690" end="01:43.040">な</span><span begin="01:43.040" end="01:43.120">い</span><span begin="01:43.120" end="01:43.220">く</span><span begin="01:43.220" end="01:43.460">せ</span><span begin="01:43.460" end="01:44.260">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">明明所谓的良知根本无法当做依凭</span></p><p begin="01:49.570" end="01:54.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:49.570" end="01:49.680">日</span><span begin="01:49.680" end="01:49.820">替</span><span begin="01:49.820" end="01:50.000">わ</span><span begin="01:50.000" end="01:50.250">り</span><span begin="01:50.250" end="01:50.915">じ</span><span begin="01:50.915" end="01:51.580">ゃ</span> <span begin="01:51.830" end="01:51.960">咲</span><span begin="01:51.960" end="01:52.090">か</span><span begin="01:52.090" end="01:52.270">せ</span><span begin="01:52.270" end="01:52.450">は</span><span begin="01:52.450" end="01:52.660">し</span><span begin="01:52.660" end="01:53.130">な</span><span begin="01:53.130" end="01:53.250">い</span><span begin="01:53.250" end="01:53.610">か</span><span begin="01:53.610" end="01:54.280">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仅凭朝夕的更迭难以让其轻易绽放</span></p><p begin="01:54.540" end="01:57.100" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:54.540" end="01:54.830">一</span><span begin="01:54.830" end="01:55.170">時</span><span begin="01:55.170" end="01:55.230">一</span><span begin="01:55.230" end="01:55.510">句</span> <span begin="01:55.510" end="01:55.710">煙</span><span begin="01:55.710" end="01:56.000">っ</span><span begin="01:56.000" end="01:56.280">た</span><span begin="01:56.280" end="01:56.380">い</span><span begin="01:56.380" end="01:56.550">ま</span><span begin="01:56.550" end="01:56.840">ま</span><span begin="01:56.840" end="01:57.100">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一时一句 在