<span begin="02:29.342" end="02:30.123">よ</span><span begin="02:30.123" end="02:30.269">り</span><span begin="02:30.269" end="02:31.325">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在这样的长夜该服用哪副药方</span></p><p begin="02:32.070" end="02:35.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:32.070" end="02:32.250">効</span><span begin="02:32.250" end="02:32.380">く</span><span begin="02:32.380" end="02:32.520">こ</span><span begin="02:32.520" end="02:32.660">と</span> <span begin="02:32.670" end="02:33.106">わ</span><span begin="02:33.106" end="02:33.543">か</span><span begin="02:33.543" end="02:33.980">っ</span><span begin="02:33.980" end="02:34.520">て</span><span begin="02:34.520" end="02:35.000">る？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">才会奏效 我心里清楚？</span></p><p begin="02:35.280" end="02:40.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="02:35.280" end="02:35.640">わ</span><span begin="02:35.640" end="02:36.000">か</span><span begin="02:36.000" end="02:36.360">っ</span><span begin="02:36.360" end="02:36.630">て</span><span begin="02:36.630" end="02:37.150">る</span> <span begin="02:37.150" end="02:37.266">わ</span><span begin="02:37.266" end="02:37.383">か</span><span begin="02:37.383" end="02:37.500">っ</span><span begin="02:37.500" end="02:37.740">て</span><span begin="02:37.740" end="02:38.390">る</span><span begin="02:38.390" end="02:38.670">の</span><span begin="02:38.670" end="02:38.910">に</span><span begin="02:38.910" end="02:39.370">何</span><span begin="02:39.370" end="02:39.560">故</span><span begin="02:39.560" end="02:40.330">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我当然十分清楚 明明心知肚明为何又会如此</span></p><p begin="02:40.670" end="02:44.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="02:40.670" end="02:41.250">気</span><span begin="02:41.250" end="02:41.680">の</span><span begin="02:41.680" end="02:42.040">迷</span><span begin="02:42.040" end="02:42.400">い</span><span begin="02:42.400" end="02:42.650">だ</span><span begin="02:42.650" end="02:4